window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Curiosity didn't kill the cat; it mutated it into a vigilante crime fighter.</b></p> <p>Dan's cats are acting weird. One has grown into a strength powerhouse, the other wants to communicate... verbally. And now other kitties have begun to go missing from his quiet suburban street. Could the man in the parka that haunts a nearby industrial estate have answers? Or perhaps it's something to do with the strange disappearing woman in the woods? Can our hero figure out the conspiracy before it turns into a catastrophe?</p> <p>There's Something Wrong with the Cats <i>is a laugh-out-loud science fiction mystery. If you like zeroes becoming heroes and twists that keep you guessing, you'll love this fun standalone novel.</i></p>"; 
